window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Opportunity doesn't always knock. Sometimes, it crash-lands.</i></p> <p>A veteran of the Resource Wars, Raze is a cyborg with a simple plan. He wants to be left alone, forever.</p> <p>Planetary scout Sevda Rem is light-years from civilization when her ship is damaged, forcing an emergency landing on an unoccupied planet. At least, it was supposed to be unoccupied....</p> <p>He's trespassing on a corporate-owned planet. She's duty bound to report him. The deck is stacked against them, but if they play their cards right, they might discover that together, they hold a winning hand.</p> <p>Publisher's note: <i>Full House</i> is a stand-alone story within the Drift series universe. It can be listened to any time after book 4, <i>Three of a Kind</i>.</p>"; 
